东区女巫前情提要...
Previously, on Witches of East End...

2
00:00:02,204 --> 00:00:05,724
你的项链 变红了 这是你最后一条命了
Your necklace, it's red. This is your last life.

3
00:00:05,725 --> 00:00:08,182
你也许应该走开了
You should probably move along now.

4
00:00:08,183 --> 00:00:10,937
你不必这么做的 我可以自己照顾自己
You didn't have to do that. I can take care of myself.

5
00:00:10,955 --> 00:00:13,491
你没什么可担心的
You have nothing to worry about.

6
00:00:13,492 --> 00:00:15,755
我只是想确定我没有成为第三者
I just want to make sure I'm not getting in the middle of something.

7
00:00:15,756 --> 00:00:17,119
只是一个吻而已 
It was just a kiss, 

8
00:00:17,120 --> 00:00:20,529
我们绝对不会告诉任何人 因为这已经结束了
and we are never, ever going to tell anyone because it's over.

9
00:00:20,530 --> 00:00:25,285
我在图书馆听到你的话了 我要一早去伦敦
I heard you at the library. I'm leaving early for London.

10
00:00:25,895 --> 00:00:28,826
我不是你母亲 你认识我 我是雅典娜
I'm not your mother. You knew me as Athena.

11
00:00:28,827 --> 00:00:31,790
- 我为什么会在这里? - 巨蛇座
- Why am I here? - Serpens clavem.

12
00:00:31,791 --> 00:00:32,955
它是一条金色的蛇 
It's a golden snake. 

13
00:00:32,956 --> 00:00:34,509
尾巴看起来像一把钥匙
The tail looks like a key.

14
00:00:34,543 --> 00:00:38,046
我要你说服你姨妈把它交出来
I need you to convince your aunt to give it back.

15
00:00:38,080 --> 00:00:40,098
只要你告诉我蛇钥匙在哪里 这一切就会结束
This will end if you tell me where the snake is.

16
00:00:40,132 --> 00:00:41,643
它已经没了
It's gone.

17
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:46,412
她说一个是你的灵魂伴侣 
She said one is your soul mate, 

18
00:00:46,413 --> 00:00:48,023
另一个 是你的冤家?
and the other, your destroyer?

19
00:00:48,057 --> 00:00:50,191
意思是其中一个会把你杀死吗?
Does that mean one of them is gonna kill you?

20
00:00:50,226 --> 00:00:52,672
这是个比喻 英格丽德 塔罗牌可是很狡猾的
It's a metaphor, Ingrid. Tarot cards are tricky that way.

21
00:00:52,673 --> 00:00:54,424
你觉得基利安是你的冤家吗?
And you think Killian is the destroyer?

22
00:00:54,425 --> 00:00:56,111
很明显啊 所有这些麻烦
Obviously. All this trouble 

23
00:00:56,112 --> 00:00:57,644
都始于我认识他的那晚
started the night I met him.

24
00:00:57,645 --> 00:01:00,935
他就是我失去达什的原因 他当然是我的冤家
He's the reason I lost Dash. Damn right he's the destroyer.

25
00:01:00,953 --> 00:01:02,437
...什么 两分钟 还...
...what, two minutes, and...

26
00:01:02,455 --> 00:01:04,318
那 你打算怎么办?
So, what are you gonna do?

27
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:07,199
我能怎么办? 达什现在在伦敦 
What can I do? Dash is in London. 

28
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,543
他都不回我电话
He's not returning any of my calls.

29
00:01:08,577 --> 00:01:11,112
他现在恨死我了... 是我活该
He hates me right now... And rightfully so.

30
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:16,776
- 请慢用 - 弗雷娅 我很抱歉
- Enjoy. - Freya, I'm so sorry.

31
00:01:16,777 --> 00:01:19,182
没事 我不会让基利安毁了我的...
It's okay. I am not gonna let Killian destroy me...

32
00:01:19,183 --> 00:01:21,556
我要把这些伤心都变成美好
I'm gonna trade all this heartbreak for good.

33
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:24,880
就像那对苦命夫妻一样 看
Like for that angry couple back there. Watch.

34
00:01:24,881 --> 00:01:26,267
...一定有什么事...  
...something that's been going on...  

35
00:01:26,268 --> 00:01:26,961
听着 我很抱歉
Look, I'm sorry.

36
00:01:26,979 --> 00:01:29,137
- 我们不要再这么做了 - 好
- Let's not do that again. - Okay.

37
00:01:29,138 --> 00:01:30,986
你刚才做了什么?
What did you just do?

38
00:01:31,021 --> 00:01:33,621
用点小心思 给他们一个"爱的突袭"
Gave 'em a "Rush of Love," with a twist.

39
00:01:33,648 --> 00:01:36,200
天哪 你太棒了
Damn, you're good.

40
00:01:36,201 --> 00:01:38,369
我的生活也许很混乱 
My life may be in shambles, 

41
00:01:38,370 --> 00:01:41,189
不过至少我能让别人高兴起来
but at least I can make someone else happy.

42
00:01:45,504 --> 00:01:47,211
花朵...
Flore...

43
00:01:47,245 --> 00:01:50,264
凋零
Pulchre.

44
00:01:50,298 --> 00:01:51,849
花朵..
Flore...

45
00:01:51,883 --> 00:01:54,752
重生
Veneficus.

46
00:02:15,709 --> 00:02:18,909
东区女巫 第一季第08集

47
00:02:22,947 --> 00:02:25,616
- 温迪 - 嘿
- Wendy. - Hey.

48
00:02:26,423 --> 00:02:29,375
- 嘿 - 怎么了?
- Hey. - What's up?

49
00:02:34,294 --> 00:02:37,163
我要给你看一样东西
I need to show you something,

50
00:02:37,181 --> 00:02:40,183
不过...
and, uh...

51
00:02:40,544 --> 00:02:43,629
我希望你不要生我的气
I don't want you to get angry with me.

52
00:02:44,665 --> 00:02:47,722
好吧 我为什么要生气呢?
Okay, why would I be angry?

53
00:02:51,645 --> 00:02:53,446
入口钥匙?!
The portal key!?

54
00:02:53,753 --> 00:02:56,682
究竟怎么回事! 你说过它已经被毁了的
What the hell! You said that was destroyed.

55
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:59,368
- 我说谎了 - 你说谎...?
- I lied. - You lied...?

56
00:02:59,403 --> 00:03:01,626
就因为这把钥匙我被杀了! 
I was killed over that key! 

57
00:03:01,627 --> 00:03:03,507
现在我只有最后一条命了
I'm on my last life now.

58
00:03:03,508 --> 00:03:05,747
- 我很抱歉 - 你很抱歉!
- I am so sorry. - You're so sorry!

59
00:03:05,748 --> 00:03:08,657
你向我保证不生气的
You promised me that you were not gonna get angry.

60
00:03:08,658 --> 00:03:09,858
不 我没有
No, I didn't.

61
00:03:09,859 --> 00:03:11,943
- 我听见你说了! - 不 我没说!
- I heard you! - No, I didn't!

62
00:03:11,944 --> 00:03:14,546
你在干什么呢 乔安娜? 怎么回事?
What are you doing, Joanna? What happened?

63
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:17,449
为什么假冒者会以为是我偷了它?
And why did the shifter think that I stole it?

64
00:03:20,169 --> 00:03:23,288
我不知道 不知道
I have no idea. I don't know.

65
00:03:23,306 --> 00:03:27,792
- 乔... - 无疑阿奇博尔德想得到它
- Jo... - Archibald wanted it, for sure.

66
00:03:27,810 --> 00:03:30,729
- 是吗? - 他甚至怀疑东西在我们这里
- Yeah? - And he even suspected that we had it,

67
00:03:30,763 --> 00:03:32,835
不过他没想出它在什么地方
but he's never figured out where it was,

68
00:03:32,836 --> 00:03:34,750
我已经把它藏了几百年了
and I've kept it hidden for centuries.

69
00:03:34,751 --> 00:03:36,835
假冒者知道我们住在哪里 乔安娜
The shifter knows where we live, Joanna.

70
00:03:36,836 --> 00:03:39,421
- 温迪 我搞砸了 - 对 你搞砸了
- Wendy, I messed up. - Yeah, you messed up.

71
00:03:39,526 --> 00:03:42,842
我们密封了入口钥匙你却告诉我它已经被毁了
You told me that thing was destroyed after we sealed the portal.

72
00:03:42,859 --> 00:03:44,018
我很相信你 
I believed you. 

73
00:03:44,019 --> 00:03:46,144
我知道 我也说了...
I know. And like I said...

74
00:03:46,162 --> 00:03:47,579
你说谎了
You lied.

75
00:03:47,613 --> 00:03:51,116
你为什么要保留巨蛇座?
Why would you keep that snake?

76
00:03:51,150 --> 00:03:52,584
它...
It's...

77
00:03:52,618 --> 00:03:55,965
很诱惑很败坏又很讨厌
Seductive and corrupting and poisonous.

78
00:03:55,966 --> 00:03:58,439
我们都知道它会对人们做出什么事
You and I both know what it does to people.

79
00:03:58,440 --> 00:04:00,691
你为什么还一直保存着它?
Why would you keep it this whole time?

80
00:04:02,845 --> 00:04:05,263
你以为你某天会用上它
You thought that you might use it again someday.

81
00:04:05,298 --> 00:04:09,634
难以置信! 你还说我鲁莽呢
Unbelievable! And you call me the reckless one.

82
00:04:09,668 --> 00:04:13,438
你知道我们再也回不去了 乔安娜
You know that we can never go back there, Joanna.

83
00:04:13,473 --> 00:04:15,237
你为什么想回到过去呢? 
Why would you want to? 

84
00:04:15,238 --> 00:04:17,150
现在我们的生活比以前好多了
Our lives so much better here.

85
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:19,989
我从没用过它 温迪 我也没打算用它
I've never used it, Wendy, I don't plan to use it,

86
00:04:20,023 --> 00:04:22,174
不过我不会把它丢掉... 
but I'm not getting rid of it... 

87
00:04:22,175 --> 00:04:24,326
这是我跟我们家族唯一的连结
It is my only connection with our home.

88
00:04:26,363 --> 00:04:28,387
温迪...
Wendy...

89
00:04:28,403 --> 00:04:31,405
我觉得这样很不好
I don't feel good about this.

90
00:04:35,538 --> 00:04:39,258
- 嘿 抱歉我迟到了 - 嘿 没事 没事
- Hey. Sorry I'm late. - Hey. Oh, no problem, no problem.

91
00:04:39,292 --> 00:04:41,877
发生什么事了? 弗雷娅的婚礼取消了吗?
So, what happened? Is Freya's wedding off?

92
00:04:41,911 --> 00:04:43,429
也许 很可能
Maybe. Probably.

93
00:04:43,463 --> 00:04:46,265
真希望我能帮上什么忙
Oh, I just wish there was something I could do to help.

94
00:04:46,299 --> 00:04:48,477
好吧 要是能让你好受点的话
Well, if it makes you feel better,

95
00:04:48,478 --> 00:04:50,436
有个人你还真能帮呢
there's someone else here that you can help.

96
00:04:50,470 --> 00:04:52,159
他们想借书吗?
Do they want to check out a book?

97
00:04:52,185 --> 00:04:54,669
貌似他想借的是你
Seems like he wants to check you out.

98
00:04:55,925 --> 00:04:58,360
那是迈克
Oh, that's just Mike.

99
00:04:58,395 --> 00:05:01,697
就是他在内战走廊救了你?
That's the guy that saved you in the Civil War aisle?

100
00:05:01,731 --> 00:05:03,532
你没告诉我他有这么帅啊
You didn't tell me how cute he was.

101
00:05:03,903 --> 00:05:06,819
- 你觉得帅吗? - 是啊
- You think so? - Yeah.

102
00:05:08,604 --> 00:05:11,606
巴布 不 我... 我又不是在逛超市
Barb, no, I'm... I'm not in the market.

103
00:05:11,624 --> 00:05:13,775
好吧 我不会说服你嫁给他
Oh, well, I'm not telling you to marry him.

104
00:05:13,793 --> 00:05:15,911
我甚至不想让你跟他约会
I'm not even telling you to date him.

105
00:05:15,945 --> 00:05:19,968
不过我希望你过去帮帮他
But I am telling you to go over there and help him.

106
00:05:22,836 --> 00:05:24,720
嘿 迈克
Hey, Mike.

107
00:05:24,754 --> 00:05:28,941
- 英格丽德 见到你很高兴 - 怎么了?
- Ingrid, I am so glad to see you. - What's going on?

108
00:05:28,942 --> 00:05:31,779
我听说你很了解东区的历史
I hear you know a lot about the history of East End.

109
00:05:31,780 --> 00:05:34,060
对 我研究过一些 你想知道什么?
I have studied some, yes. What do you want to know?

110
00:05:34,061 --> 00:05:35,384
所有的一切
Everything.

111
00:05:35,385 --> 00:05:37,487
我有一部历史虚构小说 
My novel is historical fiction, 

112
00:05:37,488 --> 00:05:39,399
正进行到二十世纪之交
set here at the turn of the 20th century,

113
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:42,237
我很希望能借用一下专家的观点
and I could really use some insight from an expert.

114
00:05:42,272 --> 00:05:46,348
我不确定能当专家 不过很乐意帮助你
Well, I'm not sure I'm an expert, but I would be happy to help.

115
00:05:46,809 --> 00:05:48,160
太棒了
Great.

116
00:05:50,962 --> 00:05:52,596
嘿
Hey.

117
00:05:54,546 --> 00:05:56,931
达什的手没事吧?
How's Dash's hand?

118
00:06:00,402 --> 00:06:02,086
我说你好
I said hello.

119
00:06:02,121 --> 00:06:05,923
这里没有龙舌兰酒了 我想楼上会有
We're out of tequila. I think there's some more upstairs.

120
00:06:07,543 --> 00:06:10,378
怎么 你就这样... 不跟我说话了吗?
So what, you're just... not gonna talk to me?

121
00:06:10,412 --> 00:06:13,157
我说话了啊 我说这里没有龙舌兰酒了
I just did. I said we're out of tequila.

122
00:06:13,171 --> 00:06:16,471
你怎么能生我的气呢?
How can you be mad at me?

123
00:06:16,472 --> 00:06:19,226
这些又不是我的错 我又没告诉达什我们的事
None of this is my fault. I didn't tell Dash what happened.

124
00:06:19,227 --> 00:06:21,041
你能诚实地看着我并且告诉我
Can you honestly look me in the eye 

125
00:06:21,042 --> 00:06:22,856
他发现之后你没觉得高兴吗?
and say you are not happy that he found out?

126
00:06:22,857 --> 00:06:24,164
这就是你希望发生的事...
This is what you wanted to have happen...

127
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,400
不准...
Stop...

128
00:06:25,401 --> 00:06:27,017
怪罪到我身上
Putting this on me.

129
00:06:27,018 --> 00:06:28,542
听着 我做了所有你要求我做的事
Look, I've done everything you asked.

130
00:06:28,543 --> 00:06:30,430
你想做朋友 我们做朋友了 
You wanted to be friends, we're friends. 

131
00:06:30,431 --> 00:06:32,172
你让我向前看 我向前看了
You told me to move on, I moved on.

132
00:06:32,724 --> 00:06:35,349
别搞得好像我毁了你的生活一样
Stop treating me like I screwed up your life.

133
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,783
就是这样! 你就是毁了我的生活!
You did! You destroyed it!

134
00:06:39,303 --> 00:06:41,891
你以为我希望我哥哥恨我吗?
You think I want my brother to hate me?

135
00:06:42,479 --> 00:06:44,339
你以为我希望你恨我吗?
You think I want you to hate me?

136
00:06:44,340 --> 00:06:45,668
我不知道你想怎么样 
I don't know what you want. 

137
00:06:45,669 --> 00:06:47,130
我想连你自己都不知道
I don't think you know what you want.

138
00:06:47,131 --> 00:06:49,659
我觉得这一切对你来说都是个游戏 
I think this whole thing is a game to you, 

139
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:50,923
我再也不想参与了
and I am not doing it anymore.

140
00:06:58,168 --> 00:06:59,600
嗨
Hi.

141
00:07:05,258 --> 00:07:06,804
艾米...
Amy...

142
00:07:06,805 --> 00:07:09,997
抱歉 我来看你工作原本是想给你个惊喜
Sorry, I thought I would surprise you at work.

143
00:07:10,553 --> 00:07:12,170
好惊喜呢
Surprise.

144
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:35,369
也许我们不应该等到日落再把它埋了
Maybe we shouldn't wait until sundown to bury it.

145
00:07:35,416 --> 00:07:37,129
也许我们本来就不应该埋它 
Maybe we shouldn't bury it at all. 

146
00:07:37,130 --> 00:07:38,447
我觉得我们应该烧了它
I think we should just burn it.

147
00:07:38,448 --> 00:07:41,336
要是我一个人处理掉这些你会觉得好受些吗?
Would you feel more comfortable if I took care of this without you?

148
00:07:41,337 --> 00:07:43,711
不 如果它不存在我才会好受些
No, I'd feel more comfortable if it didn't exist.

149
00:07:44,555 --> 00:07:47,540
你看见它是怎么对待我们父亲的
You saw what it did to our father.

150
00:07:48,516 --> 00:07:50,596
它把他体内所有的东西都毁了
It killed everything good inside of him.

151
00:07:50,597 --> 00:07:54,238
你不用盯着我看 我们不会销毁它的
We're not getting rid of it, so you can stop looking at me like that.

152
00:07:54,272 --> 00:07:55,683
听着 乔安娜 
Listen, Joanna, 

153
00:07:55,684 --> 00:07:58,909
我... 我理解你为什么保留着它
I... I understand why you kept it.

154
00:07:58,944 --> 00:08:00,811
我真的理解
I do.

155
00:08:00,829 --> 00:08:03,414
你以为要是你等得足够久 也许某一天
You thought if you waited long enough, that maybe someday

156
00:08:03,448 --> 00:08:05,364
你就能利用它再见到弗雷德里克
you could use it so you could see Frederick again.

157
00:08:05,365 --> 00:08:07,047
我不想谈弗雷德里克  
I don't want to talk about Frederick.  

158
00:08:07,048 --> 00:08:08,729
你从来不想谈弗雷德里克
You never want to talk about him.

159
00:08:08,958 --> 00:08:10,592
我知道你想他
I know that you miss him.

160
00:08:10,626 --> 00:08:14,121
我不想谈论这些 我就不应该告诉你钥匙的事
I don't want to talk about it. I should never have told you about the key.

161
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:16,548
别管它了 我会处理好它的
So just leave it alone, and I'll take care of it.

162
00:08:43,864 --> 00:08:46,208
温迪...
Wendy...

163
00:09:13,781 --> 00:09:16,184
你干什么了?!
What did you do?!

164
00:09:16,211 --> 00:09:18,396
它攻击我 快把它弄下来
It attacked me. Get it off right now.

165
00:09:18,431 --> 00:09:20,568
- 哎呦! - 我在弄呢 我不想弄伤你
- Ow, ow, ow! - I'm trying. I don't want to hurt you.

166
00:09:20,599 --> 00:09:23,401
到底怎么回事! 你看它的眼睛了吗?
What the hell happened! Did you look in its eyes?

167
00:09:23,436 --> 00:09:25,928
你知道不该看它的眼睛的
You know you are not supposed to look in its eyes.

168
00:09:25,929 --> 00:09:29,056
好了 我现在 实在是没心情听你说教
Okay, I am really, really not in the mood for one of your lectures right now.

169
00:09:29,074 --> 00:09:30,900
解除巨蛇
Dimitte serpens.

170
00:09:30,901 --> 00:09:33,111
这条蛇是纯粹邪恶的载体
This snake is a powerful vessel of pure evil.

171
00:09:33,112 --> 00:09:35,167
我觉得我们需要一些更厉害的东西 
I think we need something a little stronger 

172
00:09:35,168 --> 00:09:36,581
而不是即兴的拉丁咒语!
than off-the-cuff Latin commands!

173
00:09:36,615 --> 00:09:38,206
我们试试讽刺吧 应该有帮助
Let's try sarcasm; that should help.

174
00:09:38,233 --> 00:09:39,701
我去拿魔书
Let me get the Grimoire.

175
00:09:39,735 --> 00:09:41,135
乔安娜
Joanna.

176
00:09:41,136 --> 00:09:43,120
看啊
Look.

177
00:09:44,874 --> 00:09:47,494
待着别动 我去把书拿来 我们会找到办法的
Stay right there. I'm getting the book. We'll figure this out.

178
00:09:47,495 --> 00:09:48,770
快点
Hurry.

179
00:10:08,481 --> 00:10:11,449
- 听着 基利安... - 天哪
- Look, Killian... - Oh, God.

180
00:10:11,484 --> 00:10:15,470
"听着 基利安"后面从来没有好结果
No good conversation ever started with "Look, Killian..."

181
00:10:15,471 --> 00:10:19,024
我喜欢你 真的 很喜欢
I really like you. I do. A lot.

182
00:10:19,143 --> 00:10:23,163
我喜欢忧郁的男生 我对他们毫无抵抗力
I have a thing for lost souls. I'm... I'm a sucker for them.

183
00:10:23,197 --> 00:10:25,513
但是我觉得我不是那个能找到你灵魂的人
But I don't think I'm the one who can find you.

184
00:10:25,514 --> 00:10:27,914
如果是因为弗雷娅 我可以告诉你...  
If this is because Freya, I told you...  

185
00:10:27,915 --> 00:10:28,635
你已经说过了
You did.

186
00:10:28,652 --> 00:10:31,297
你说过你对她没感觉
You told me that you don't have feelings for her.

187
00:10:31,298 --> 00:10:35,792
你可以对我撒谎 但你不能对自己撒谎
And you can lie to me if you want, but you should stop lying to yourself.

188
00:10:40,646 --> 00:10:42,280
好运 基利安
Good luck, Killian.

189
00:10:53,486 --> 00:10:55,454
你们还有什么书呢?
Okay, what else have you got?

190
00:10:55,488 --> 00:10:56,788
- 不是吧 - 说来听听
- Come on. - Hit me.

191
00:10:56,823 --> 00:10:58,403
这些你都看完了吗?  
You finished those already?  

192
00:10:58,404 --> 00:10:59,983
我看书做笔记都非常快的
I am an unbelievably fast note-taker.

193
00:10:59,984 --> 00:11:01,796
这算是我的天赋吧
It's... it's quite a skill.

194
00:11:01,797 --> 00:11:04,696
我不知道我们这儿还有多少关于东区的历史书
I don't know how many more history books on East End that we have.

195
00:11:04,714 --> 00:11:07,121
事实上我在找一些关于...
I'm actually looking for something more about...

196
00:11:07,122 --> 00:11:10,784
神灵 巫术 诅咒 幽灵一类的东西
The occult. Witchcraft, curses, spirits, that kind of thing.

197
00:11:10,785 --> 00:11:11,859
为什么?
Why?

198
00:11:11,885 --> 00:11:13,555
我想你一定已经意识到了
Well, I'm sure you're already aware of this,

199
00:11:13,589 --> 00:11:16,975
这个小镇的神话传说有很长的历史了
but this town has a long history of supernatural legends,

200
00:11:17,009 --> 00:11:20,211
从早期的殖民者到焚烧女巫再到...
from the early settlers to the witch burnings on to...

201
00:11:20,229 --> 00:11:22,052
费尔黑文阿奇博尔德・布朗宁和他的信徒
Archibald Browning and his cult at Fair Haven.

202
00:11:22,053 --> 00:11:24,349
东区一直以东部海岸
You know, East End is also famous for being one

203
00:11:24,383 --> 00:11:27,352
南瓜生长最好的小镇而出名
of the best pumpkin-growing towns on the Eastern Seaboard.

204
00:11:29,071 --> 00:11:32,324
英格丽德写过一篇关于巫术的论文
Uh, Ingrid wrote her dissertation about witchcraft.

205
00:11:32,358 --> 00:11:34,567
有意思 她... 没有跟我提过
Interesting. She didn't... mention it to me.

206
00:11:34,568 --> 00:11:36,703
除非我很讨厌某人 否则我不会跟别人聊
It's not something I usually slip into conversation

207
00:11:36,729 --> 00:11:37,992
这些事情的
unless I want to bore someone.

208
00:11:37,993 --> 00:11:39,744
- 她也会巫术 - 巴布 别说了
- She also does witchcraft. - Barb, stop.

209
00:11:39,778 --> 00:11:41,688
- 不 巴布 接着说 - 我真是太傻了
- No, Barb, continue. - This is stupid.

210
00:11:41,697 --> 00:11:43,497
她让我怀孕了
She got me pregnant.

211
00:11:43,532 --> 00:11:45,802
不 这听起来不太对
Okay. No, that sounds wrong.

212
00:11:45,803 --> 00:11:49,244
我意思是她念了一个怀孕的咒语我才怀孕的
I meant she did a fertility spell for me that made it possible.

213
00:11:49,245 --> 00:11:51,372
那咒语是假的 是我在网上学的
It was a fake spell I got off the Internet

214
00:11:51,373 --> 00:11:52,990
说不定是一个十一岁的孩子写的
probably written by an 11-year-old boy.

215
00:11:53,008 --> 00:11:54,925
跟你怀孕没任何关系
It had nothing to do with you getting pregnant.

216
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:56,493
根本没有巫术这回事
There's no such thing as witchcraft.

217
00:11:56,511 --> 00:11:58,262
好吧 你跟我肚子里这个
Well, tell that to this thing inside me

218
00:11:58,296 --> 00:12:00,831
每天早上让我呕吐的小家伙说吧
that makes me throw up every morning.

219
00:12:00,849 --> 00:12:02,932
她很搞笑
She's funny.

220
00:12:02,965 --> 00:12:04,900
看起来我们有很多东西可以聊
Sounds like we have a lot more to talk about.

221
00:12:04,934 --> 00:12:07,569
事实上 不行 我现在还有很多工作要做
Uh, actually, no. I got a lot of work to do right now.

222
00:12:07,604 --> 00:12:09,321
我哪儿也不去
Well, I'm not going anywhere.

223
00:12:10,243 --> 00:12:12,457
- 好吧 - 那我们待会儿聊
- Okay. - So, we can talk later.

224
00:12:12,458 --> 00:12:14,622
- 好的 - 好的
- Yes. - All right.

225
00:12:25,121 --> 00:12:27,845
我刚刚看到艾米了 她去哪儿了?  
Didn't I just see Amy? Where is she? 

226
00:12:27,846 --> 00:12:29,359
她走了 刚跟她分手了
She left. Just broke up with her.

227
00:12:29,377 --> 00:12:30,789
什么? 为什么?
What? Why?

228
00:12:30,790 --> 00:12:34,131
我想她要的是一段认真的恋爱 而我...
Well, I felt like she was interested in something serious and...

229
00:12:34,166 --> 00:12:35,920
不够认真
I'm not.

230
00:12:36,379 --> 00:12:38,864
你在做什么呀 基利安?
What are you doing, Killian?

231
00:12:38,984 --> 00:12:41,236
- 什么意思? - 我是说 这儿
- What do you mean? - I mean, here.

232
00:12:41,237 --> 00:12:43,707
你的人生 你怎么还能在这儿呢?
With your life. Why are you even still here?

233
00:12:43,708 --> 00:12:45,976
你怎么能在伤害了一个人之后还在这儿呢?
Why be here at all if you're just hurting people?

234
00:12:46,011 --> 00:12:49,563
弗雷娅 我觉得你没有资格批评我
I don't think you're in a position to judge me, Freya.

235
00:12:53,401 --> 00:12:55,935
弗雷娅・波尚在这儿吗?  
Is there a Freya Beauchamp here?  

236
00:12:55,936 --> 00:12:57,105
是的 在那边
Yeah, just over there.

237
00:12:58,940 --> 00:13:01,001
这是给你的
These are for you.

238
00:13:01,002 --> 00:13:03,453
- 在这儿签字 - 谢谢
- I just need you to sign. - Thanks.

239
00:13:06,865 --> 00:13:08,332
我的天...
Oh, my...

240
00:13:13,544 --> 00:13:15,660
我的天呐 是达什送的
Oh, my God. They're from Dash.

241
00:13:15,661 --> 00:13:17,708
你确定吗? 卡片上又没有名字
You sure about that? No name on the card.

242
00:13:17,742 --> 00:13:20,544
当然是达什送的 还能是谁呢?
Of course they're from Dash. Who else would they be from?

243
00:13:22,413 --> 00:13:24,859
天呐
Oh, my God.

244
00:13:30,806 --> 00:13:32,223
找到了
Got it.

245
00:13:32,257 --> 00:13:34,225
温迪 别着急
Wendy, don't worry.

246
00:13:34,259 --> 00:13:36,143
我有办法了
I have an idea.

247
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,566
温迪...?
Wendy...?

248
00:13:48,657 --> 00:13:50,457
基利安
Killian.

249
00:13:50,492 --> 00:13:52,126
妈妈
Hey, Mom.

250
00:13:52,713 --> 00:13:55,629
- 你可以走了吗? - 可以了 弗雷娅
- Are you ready to go? - Yeah, sure. Freya.

251
00:13:55,664 --> 00:13:57,916
我现在要出去一下 一小时后回来
I'm going out on my break. Be back in an hour.

252
00:13:58,307 --> 00:14:00,467
佩内洛普 很高兴见到你
Penelope, it's so nice to see you.

253
00:14:00,502 --> 00:14:03,754
亲爱的 你还好吗?
Dear, are you all right?

254
00:14:03,788 --> 00:14:06,557
- 你看起来很糟糕 - 什么?
- You look terrible. - What?

255
00:14:06,591 --> 00:14:09,625
- 说真的 你怎么啦? - 你说什么?
- Seriously, what's wrong? - What do you mean?

256
00:14:09,626 --> 00:14:12,015
首先 你一直在... 发抖
Well, for one thing, you keep... swaying.

257
00:14:12,041 --> 00:14:14,315
- 是吗? - 你看上去脸都青了
- Oh, I do? - You look positively green.

258
00:14:14,349 --> 00:14:16,433
跟我来 我带你回家
Come with me. I'm taking you home.

259
00:14:16,467 --> 00:14:19,027
我... 我还没下班呢
Oh, I... My shift isn't over.

260
00:14:19,028 --> 00:14:20,609
跟我走吧
I insist.

261
00:14:20,655 --> 00:14:22,239
我想基利安会替你一会儿的
I'm sure Killian can cover for you.

262
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,929
我们晚点再吃午饭吧
We'll have to take a rain check on our lunch.

263
00:14:23,930 --> 00:14:25,897
好的 当然了 没问题
Yeah, of course. No problem.

264
00:14:26,355 --> 00:14:27,944
但是我还没有下班
But I can't leave work.

265
00:14:27,945 --> 00:14:29,530
你再待下去就要生病了
You can't stay here if you're getting sick.

266
00:14:29,531 --> 00:14:30,981
赶紧走吧 亲爱的
Now come on, dear.

267
00:14:32,182 --> 00:14:35,744
我保证我会好好照顾你的
I promise to take very good care of you.

268
00:14:42,677 --> 00:14:44,661
- 你还好吧? - 是的
- You okay? - Yeah.

269
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:47,681
我找到一个可能有用的咒语
I found a spell that may work.

270
00:14:47,716 --> 00:14:50,684
需要的东西都有 但是我要... 准备一下
I have what we need but I'll need to... prepare.

271
00:14:50,719 --> 00:14:53,804
如果我们做的对的话也许可以留下这把钥匙
I think we can save the key if we get it right.

272
00:14:53,838 --> 00:14:56,340
我觉得没这个必要
I don't think that'll be necessary.

273
00:14:56,506 --> 00:14:57,849
温迪...  
Wendy...  

274
00:14:57,850 --> 00:15:00,344
这把钥匙可以解决我们的问题
This key is the answer to our problems.

275
00:15:00,345 --> 00:15:02,179
用它我们就可以回家了 
We can use it to go back home.  

276
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:03,180
温迪 停下来
Wendy, stop.

277
00:15:03,198 --> 00:15:04,949
毒液正在控制你
The venom's getting to you.

278
00:15:04,950 --> 00:15:06,708
我们刚刚谈过了 我们不能回去
We just talked about it. We can't go back.

279
00:15:06,709 --> 00:15:08,135
或许现在已经安全了
Maybe it's safe by now.

280
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:10,880
看着我 那里永远都不会安全的 
Look at me. It'll never be safe. 

281
00:15:10,881 --> 00:15:12,337
所以我还没用巨蛇
That's why I haven't used the serpent.

282
00:15:12,338 --> 00:15:14,245
也许你错了呢  
Maybe you're wrong. 

283
00:15:14,246 --> 00:15:17,107
你知道我们不是自愿离开的
You know we didn't leave by choice.

284
00:15:17,108 --> 00:15:20,774
父亲当权的时候把我们放逐到这个世界
Our father banished us to this world when he came into power.

285
00:15:20,775 --> 00:15:21,974
- 但是... - 不!
- But... - No!

286
00:15:21,975 --> 00:15:25,267
他说如果我们回去仙宫 他就会杀了我们
He said if we ever returned to Asgard, he will kill us.

287
00:15:25,301 --> 00:15:27,128
也许他变了呢
But maybe he's changed.

288
00:15:27,152 --> 00:15:30,154
- 他不会变的 - 你不知道
- He hasn't changed. - You don't know that.

289
00:15:30,417 --> 00:15:32,585
我只剩一条命了 乔安娜 
I have one life left, Joanna, 

290
00:15:32,586 --> 00:15:34,935
我不想浪费在这儿 我想回家
and I don't want to spend it here. I want to go home.

291
00:15:35,046 --> 00:15:38,815
- 你是永生的 你不懂 - 温迪 听我说
- You're immortal. You don't understand. - Wendy, please listen,

292
00:15:38,936 --> 00:15:40,522
你现在要集中精力
I need you to focus.

293
00:15:40,523 --> 00:15:42,974
- 如果我打开入口... - 不!
- If I could just get to the portal... - No!

294
00:15:42,992 --> 00:15:45,426
绝对不能
Absolutely not.

295
00:15:45,661 --> 00:15:47,122
如果打开入口 
If that portal opens, 

296
00:15:47,123 --> 00:15:50,464
我们不知道另一边会过来什么东西!
we have no idea what may come through from the other side!

297
00:15:52,903 --> 00:15:56,573
那条蛇正在诱惑你达到它的目的
The snake is seducing you to get what it wants.

298
00:15:56,574 --> 00:15:59,235
它的目的就是打开入口  
It only wants to open the portal.  

299
00:15:59,236 --> 00:16:00,788
那也是我希望的
That's all I want.

300
00:16:00,789 --> 00:16:03,070
我想回家 那儿比这里要好
I miss my home. It was better there.

301
00:16:03,071 --> 00:16:06,975
我也想 温迪 但那已经不是以前的样子了
I miss it, too, Wendy, but it's not the same place anymore.

302
00:16:07,356 --> 00:16:09,790
- 妈咪嘛咪哄! - 不!
- Claude ianuas! - No!

303
00:16:14,175 --> 00:16:16,096
乔安娜...!
Joanna...!

304
00:16:16,936 --> 00:16:18,561
乔安娜!
Joanna!

305
00:16:19,851 --> 00:16:21,575
妈咪嘛咪哄!
Aperite!

306
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:28,121
你这个贱人
You are such a bitch.

307
00:16:35,173 --> 00:16:37,658
成熟点吧 乔安娜
Grow up, Joanna.

308
00:16:38,261 --> 00:16:41,474
你不能把我永远困在这儿
You can't keep me in here forever.

309
00:16:45,528 --> 00:16:49,020
我会解开咒语的 你知道我一定会的
I will break this spell eventually. You know I will.

310
00:16:54,225 --> 00:16:56,193
这与你无关
This has nothing to do with you.

311
00:17:00,181 --> 00:17:02,041
我是在帮助你  
I'm trying to help you.  

312
00:17:02,042 --> 00:17:04,368
想帮助我就让我走!
You can help me by letting me go!

313
00:17:10,041 --> 00:17:13,026
我们一定得把这东西从你身上取下来
We have got to get this thing off of you.

314
00:17:13,044 --> 00:17:16,163
你在开玩笑吗?!
Are you kidding me?!

315
00:17:18,249 --> 00:17:20,551
你一点都不关心我
You don't care about me.

316
00:17:20,585 --> 00:17:23,829
你一百多年没有跟我说话
You didn't speak to me for over a hundred years.

317
00:17:24,923 --> 00:17:27,208
你是个冷血的贱人
I guess you're a coldhearted bitch.

318
00:17:27,231 --> 00:17:29,977
去问问弗雷德里克
Just ask Frederick.

319
00:17:30,011 --> 00:17:33,814
对了 你不能 因为你抛弃他了
Oh, that's right. You can't. Because you left him behind.

320
00:17:33,848 --> 00:17:35,482
你抛弃了你唯一的儿子
You abandoned your only son.

321
00:17:35,517 --> 00:17:38,018
- 事情不是那样的 - 不是吗?
- That is not true. - It's not?

322
00:17:38,052 --> 00:17:39,820
你没有抛弃他吗?
You didn't abandon him?

323
00:17:39,854 --> 00:17:44,165
是他不跟我们走 你知道他背叛我了
He refused to come with us. You know that he was turned against me.

324
00:17:44,526 --> 00:17:46,994
你知道吗 对某些人来说...
You know, for somebody...

325
00:17:47,028 --> 00:17:49,830
说起来是养育
supposedly so nurturing,

326
00:17:49,864 --> 00:17:52,899
你所做的就只是毁掉别人
all you seem to do is destroy people.

327
00:17:52,917 --> 00:17:55,902
这就是你不能谈起弗雷德里克的原因
That's why you can't talk about Frederick.

328
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:59,289
因为你无法改变你对他所做的事
Because you can't deal with what you did to him.

329
00:18:00,592 --> 00:18:04,928
或者你只是... 毫不关心
Or maybe you... just don't care.

330
00:18:06,715 --> 00:18:09,098
你这话太伤人了... 温迪
It broke my heart, Wendy.

331
00:18:09,099 --> 00:18:12,753
我没有一天不后悔把他留在那
There's not a day that goes by that I don't regret leaving him there.

332
00:18:12,771 --> 00:18:14,421
你觉得如果你告诉女孩们
What do you think the girls are gonna say

333
00:18:14,439 --> 00:18:17,691
你撇下了她们的哥哥她们会怎么想?
when I tell them that you left their brother behind?

334
00:18:17,726 --> 00:18:19,777
- 够了 - 那就对了
