妈咪嘛咪哄
Dona mihi...

457
00:25:33,105 --> 00:25:34,940
妈咪嘛咪哄
...ero.

458
00:25:44,784 --> 00:25:47,252
你真的要惹恼我了 温迪
You're starting to really piss me off, Wendy.

459
00:25:47,286 --> 00:25:49,454
马上结束吧!
This ends right now!

460
00:25:49,472 --> 00:25:53,225
会的... 但不是你希望的那样
Oh, it will... But not the way you hope.

461
00:25:53,259 --> 00:25:56,327
你一直拿着这把钥匙!
You had this key the whole time!

462
00:25:56,346 --> 00:26:00,775
我们没必要困在这 这个困扰我们的地方
We didn't have to be stuck here, where we're persecuted,

463
00:26:00,776 --> 00:26:02,976
这个需要隐藏我们本质的地方
where we have to hide our true nature.

464
00:26:02,977 --> 00:26:05,062
你为什么不想回去?!
Why don't you want to go back?!

465
00:26:05,096 --> 00:26:07,567
因为我们在这比那更安全  
Because we're safer here than there.  

466
00:26:07,568 --> 00:26:08,899
不会持续太久的
Not for long.

467
00:26:08,933 --> 00:26:10,491
妈咪嘛咪哄!
Axicia volant!

468
00:26:13,179 --> 00:26:15,163
反应很快嘛 亲爱的
Ooh, nice reflexes, babe.

469
00:26:15,164 --> 00:26:18,677
你带那个东西过久 你就不再是你了
You keep that thing on much longer, you'll never be yourself again.

470
00:26:18,993 --> 00:26:22,162
这么久毒素已经深入你的血液了
It's been pumping poison into your veins this whole time.

471
00:26:22,188 --> 00:26:23,978
那你必须毁了它才能从我身上取下来
Then you'll have to destroy it to get it off me,

472
00:26:23,979 --> 00:26:26,806
我知道为了弗雷德里克你不会的
and I know that you can't because of Frederick.

473
00:26:27,368 --> 00:26:29,936
我猜你很为难 对吗?
So I guess you're in a bit of a pickle, aren't you?

474
00:26:29,937 --> 00:26:33,786
- 温迪... 别这样 - 妈咪嘛咪哄!
- Wendy... come on. - Omnia telavolant!

475
00:26:48,005 --> 00:26:49,439
妈咪嘛咪哄
Axicia...

476
00:26:49,474 --> 00:26:51,970
妈咪嘛咪哄
interficiam serpens.

477
00:26:57,769 --> 00:27:01,706
我父亲在秘鲁挖出来的这个
My father found this on a dig in Peru.

478
00:27:01,740 --> 00:27:04,242
他相信这个...
He believed that this...

479
00:27:04,276 --> 00:27:07,082
是去仙宫的地图
was a map to Asgard.

480
00:27:07,496 --> 00:27:10,715
你看 它已经退色了
As you can see, though, it's very faded.

481
00:27:11,142 --> 00:27:13,672
这是个很有意思的符号
That is an interesting symbol.

482
00:27:13,673 --> 00:27:17,203
- 他认为那个是什么意思? - 他不知道
- What did he think that meant? - Uh, he didn't know.

483
00:27:17,204 --> 00:27:19,214
他相信这个和巫术有关 
He thought it had something to do with witchcraft, 

484
00:27:19,215 --> 00:27:21,225
但是... 他没能破解
but... he couldn't crack it.

485
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:23,294
我也没弄明白 但是...
I haven't figured it out, either, but...

486
00:27:23,312 --> 00:27:25,263
这不会妨碍我接着尝试
that's not gonna stop me from trying.

487
00:27:45,617 --> 00:27:48,669
嗨? 有人在家吗?
Hello? Anybody home?

488
00:27:50,133 --> 00:27:52,518
妈妈 你在吗?
Mom, are you here?

489
00:27:53,825 --> 00:27:56,866
- 怎么了? - 快点! 拿你的医药箱!
- What's going on? - Hurry! Get your medical bag!

490
00:27:59,325 --> 00:28:02,708
看来为了这本书你的确找了很多材料
Well, it sure seems like you have a lot of material for this book of yours.

491
00:28:02,709 --> 00:28:03,818
我知道
I know.

492
00:28:03,827 --> 00:28:05,944
我也许该继续
I should probably get going.

493
00:28:05,945 --> 00:28:08,213
我还有一本书要看
There's just one more book I need to look at.

494
00:28:08,214 --> 00:28:10,106
我马上回来
I'll be right back.

495
00:28:18,648 --> 00:28:20,649
妈咪嘛咪哄
Ostende te.

496
00:28:29,859 --> 00:28:31,994
妈咪嘛咪哄
Absconde Te.

497
00:28:32,028 --> 00:28:33,923
- 看到什么有趣的东西了吗? - 没有
- See anything interesting on there? - No.

498
00:28:33,924 --> 00:28:37,045
这个... 你说得对 这个太旧了
It, uh... I think you're right, it's just too worn out.

499
00:28:37,046 --> 00:28:38,246
是啊
Yeah.

500
00:28:41,481 --> 00:28:43,203
她怎么了?
What's wrong with her?

501
00:28:43,204 --> 00:28:44,222
我基本感觉不到心跳 
I can barely feel the pulse. 

502
00:28:44,223 --> 00:28:45,343
这里到底发生什么事了?
What the hell happened here?

503
00:28:45,344 --> 00:28:47,059
我... 我不知道 
I... I don't know. 

504
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:49,460
我们当时在喝茶 她突然就倒了
We were having tea, and she just suddenly collapsed.

505
00:28:49,461 --> 00:28:51,128
- 多久了? - 我不知道
- How long ago? - I don't know,

